item.title: A Fast Guide to Using SDXL with Conf UI
item.description: Overview This post provides a quick tutorial on using the SDXL AI model with Conf UI for fast high-quality image generation. Steps Download and install Conf UI from the provided link. Be sure to update to the latest version. Open the Conf UI canvas and import the pre-made SDXL workflow provided.
